<s snum=55>With the metal shutters closed, the dining room was so dark that it seemed still night in there.</s>
<s snum=56>One of the drawing-room shutters was partly open and he made out the shapes of chairs and sofas, which seemed to be upholstered in brown or russet velvet.</s>
<s snum=57>The curtains were of the same material, and there were some big oil paintings- portraits in the style of Lancret and Boucher.</s>
