<s snum=81>Rather than sit around waiting for the suitcases to be delivered, they had gone sight-seeing.</s>
<s snum=82>They went to the Flea Market, expecting to find the treasures of Europe, and found instead a duplication of that long double row of booths in Tours.</s>
